{"tid":1323201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果日報：旺角女子被指偷拍示威者遭包圍 涉案3男女被控禁錮非禮","createTime":"2019-07-16T07:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T07:18:10.000Z","uid":275574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"08720b578d2b97d4c2784f77d21028dcc64ec42a","tid":1323201,"uid":275574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"九龍區上周日遊行後爆發衝突，其間一名短髮女子被指潛入人群中偷拍示威者的容貌，遭示威者包圍，女事主翌日報案。警方事後拘捕涉案2男1女，年齡介乎23至31歲，分別涉嫌非法禁錮、襲擊、非法集結及非禮。3人今日被警方暫控以合共一項非法禁錮罪，當中一名31歲被捕男子亦被暫控以一項非禮罪。案件將於今日下午在九龍城裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190716/59829367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190716%2F59829367&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=383da1d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190716%2F59829367&h=db8f6295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190716/59829367</a>"}]}